INSERT INTO `news_posts` VALUES (4,'Malnutrition ‘prevalent’ in children in urban settings: Study',0,'2020-03-17 09:47:27','2021-05-01 19:54:05','malnutrition-prevalent-in-children-in-urban-settings-study','active','Ishwor BK of Mainabagar was only 1.75kg at birth. Ishwor, who turned 26 months on February 27, weighed only 9.3kg. As the baby was gaining weight at a much slower rate than expected, his mother Muna took him to Lumbini Provincial Hospital in Butwal for a','<div>Ishwor BK of Mainabagar was only 1.75kg at birth. Ishwor, who turned 26 months on February 27, weighed only 9.3kg. As the baby was gaining weight at a much slower rate than expected, his mother Muna took him to Lumbini Provincial Hospital in Butwal for a general check-up.</div><div><br></div><div>Doctors advised Muna to admit her son to the hospital’s Child Nutrition Rehabilitation Home for treatment. Eighteen days into treatment, Ishwor weighed 10.3kg.</div><div><br></div>',4,'News-20200317105025585.jpg','Lumbini','Annapurna post','state3',1,'2020-04-10 00:00:00'),(5,'Government bans entry of all passengers, including Nepalis, from midnight March 20',0,'2020-03-17 09:52:14','2020-04-08 19:41:52',NULL,'active','The government has banned all passengers, including Nepalis, from entering Nepal from European Union territories, including the United Kingdom, West Asia, Gulf countries and countries like Iran, Turkey, Malaysia, South Korea and Japan. The ban will come i','&lt;p&gt;The government has banned all passengers, including Nepalis, from entering Nepal from European Union territories, including the United Kingdom, West Asia, Gulf countries and countries like Iran, Turkey, Malaysia, South Korea and Japan. The ban will come into effect from March 20 midnight and will remain in place until April 15.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;All passengers transiting in these locations are also prohibited.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Movement from China, however, has remained inexplicably open.&lt;/p&gt;',11,'News-20200408053538197.jpg','Bhaktapur','Kantipur','state1',1,'2020-04-10 00:00:00'),(6,' SEE postponed, public gatherings of more than 25 barred, and gyms, film halls closed',0,'2020-03-19 12:49:03','2020-04-08 15:34:34',NULL,'active','The government’s decisions are aimed at limiting the spread of Covid-19, which has now invaded over 170 countries and killed more than 8,000 people.\r\n SEE postponed, public gatherings of more than 25 barred, and gyms, film halls closed\r\nFile photo of stud','&lt;p&gt;The government&rsquo;s decisions are aimed at limiting the spread of Covid-19, which has now invaded over 170 countries and killed more than 8,000 people.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;SEE postponed, public gatherings of more than 25 barred, and gyms, film halls closed&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;File photo of students taking Secondary Education Examinations.&amp;nbsp; Angad Dhakal/TKP&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;bookmark&lt;/p&gt;',11,'News-20200408052735692.jpg','Kathmandu','Kantipur','all',1,'2020-02-04 00:00:00'),(7,'COVID-19 is declared as Pandemic',0,'2020-03-19 12:53:20','2020-04-08 12:51:26',NULL,'active','Nepalis wearing masks is not a new thing. Thanks to the poor air quality, a lot of Nepalis over the course of the past few years, especially in Kathmandu, have become used to using masks. But how many actually know how to use them? Do many know that surgi','&lt;p&gt;Nepalis wearing masks is not a new thing. Thanks to the poor air quality, a lot of Nepalis over the course of the past few years, especially in Kathmandu, have become used to using masks. But how many actually know how to use them? Do many know that surgical and cloth masks are not nearly as effective as assumed? Should everyone be wearing masks at a time when there is such acute shortage? Or should they be saved for those who actually need them?&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;',20,'News-20200408025126835.png','Lalitpur','Kantipur','all',1,'2020-04-09 00:00:00'),(8,'Investors warned not to rush into travel and leisure stocks',0,'2020-04-08 15:52:39','2020-04-08 15:55:30',NULL,'active','Investors are being warned about piling money into the travel and leisure sectors after their recent surge.','&lt;p class=&quot;story-body__introduction&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.375; margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Investors are being warned about piling money into the travel and leisure sectors after their recent surge.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin: 23px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Travel and leisure stocks including airlines and cinema chains have been hit hard by the coronavirus lockdowns and travel restrictions.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin: 18px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;While their valuations have plummeted across the board, some stocks have seen their share prices rocket this week.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin: 18px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;On Tuesday, cinema chain Cineworld shot up almost 50% while cruise ship operator Carnival surged more than 20%.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin: 18px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Cineworld, the world\'s second biggest cinema chain, announced bosses had waived salaries and bonuses as part of a survival plan to tackle coronavirus lockdowns.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin: 18px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Admitting the current situation was &quot;extremely challenging&quot;, Cineworld said it had scrapped a planned dividend to shareholders for the last quarter of 2019.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin: 18px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;But its share price shot up 49% on the London Stock Exchange despite its bleak outlook, with more than 780 cinemas closed across 10 countries.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin: 18px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Another travel and leisure stock, cruise ship operator Carnival, also saw a big price rise on Tuesday, after Saudi Arabia\'s sovereign wealth fund took a 8.2% stake in it.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin: 18px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Carnival\'s share price rose 11% on the New York Stock Exchange and 22% on the London Stock Exchange&lt;/p&gt;',17,'News-20200408055530601.jpg','Kathmandu','BBC','state3',1,'2020-02-02 00:00:00'),(9,'Disneyland won’t refund coronavirus tickets, but you can postpone',0,'2020-04-08 16:03:06',NULL,NULL,'active','Star Wars: Rise of the Resistance opened in January. Disneyland has been closed since March 14 because of the coronavirus pandemic.','&lt;p style=&quot;background-repeat: no-repeat; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;If you bought tickets for a&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;Link&quot; href=&quot;https://disneyland.disney.go.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;background-repeat: no-repeat; touch-action: manipulation; color: var(--primaryBodyLinkColor); text-decoration-line: underline;&quot;&gt;Disneyland&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;visit on a date that coincides with closures prompted by the coronavirus pandemic, don&rsquo;t expect to get a refund. Instead, the Anaheim theme park is allowing ticket holders to postpone the date of their visit.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;Enhancement&quot; data-align-center=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;background-repeat: no-repeat; clear: both; margin: 30px 0px; width: 619px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;ps-promo class=&quot;PromoSmall&quot; data-content-type=&quot;article&quot; style=&quot;background-repeat: no-repeat; display: block; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--secondaryColor3); border-top: 1px solid var(--secondaryColor3); padding: 20px 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;PromoSmall-wrapper&quot; style=&quot;background-repeat: no-repeat; display: flex; flex-direction: row;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;PromoSmall-media&quot; style=&quot;background-repeat: no-repeat; position: relative; margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; flex-shrink: 0; max-width: 110px; order: 1; width: 110px;&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;Link&quot; aria-label=&quot;DOT tells airlines to refund canceled flights, but don&rsquo;t count on cash just yet&quot; href=&quot;https://www.latimes.com/travel/story/2020-04-06/airlines-coronavirus-refund-canceled-flights&quot; style=&quot;background-repeat: no-repeat; touch-action: manipulation; color: inherit; display: block; position: relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;Image&quot; alt=&quot;508393_ME-LAX-CORONAVIRUS-SCREENING_KKN_30431.JPG&quot; width=&quot;840&quot; height=&quot;560&quot; data-src=&quot;https://ca-times.brightspotcdn.com/dims4/default/61f0980/2147483647/strip/true/crop/6000x4000+0+0/resize/840x560!/quality/90/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcalifornia-times-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fff%2F5f%2F5c257cc74cc9ae76155a86fa06bf%2Fla-photos-1staff-508393-me-lax-coronavirus-screening-kkn-30431.JPG&quot; src=&quot;https://ca-times.brightspotcdn.com/dims4/default/61f0980/2147483647/strip/true/crop/6000x4000+0+0/resize/840x560!/quality/90/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcalifornia-times-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fff%2F5f%2F5c257cc74cc9ae76155a86fa06bf%2Fla-photos-1staff-508393-me-lax-coronavirus-screening-kkn-30431.JPG&quot; style=&quot;background-repeat: no-repeat; display: block; height: auto; max-width: 100%; width: 110px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;PromoSmall-content&quot; style=&quot;background-repeat: no-repeat; order: 2;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;PromoSmall-titleContainer&quot; style=&quot;background-repeat: no-repeat;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;PromoSmall-category&quot; style=&quot;background-repeat: no-repeat; color: var(--secondaryTextColor); font-family: var(--secondaryHeadlineFont),Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: var(--label-1); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 10px;&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;Link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.latimes.com/travel&quot; style=&quot;background-repeat: no-repeat; touch-action: manipulation; color: inherit;&quot;&gt;TRAVEL&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;PromoSmall-title&quot; style=&quot;background-repeat: no-repeat; font-family: var(--primaryHeadlineFont),Times New Roman,Times,serif; font-size: var(--title-5); line-height: 1.17; letter-spacing: -0.2px; font-weight: 600;&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;Link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.latimes.com/travel/story/2020-04-06/airlines-coronavirus-refund-canceled-flights&quot; style=&quot;background-repeat: no-repeat; touch-action: manipulation; color: inherit;&quot;&gt;DOT tells airlines to refund canceled flights, but don&rsquo;t count on cash just yet&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;PromoSmall-timestamp&quot; data-date=&quot;April 6, 2020&quot; data-shouldshowdate=&quot;true&quot; data-shouldshowtime=&quot;true&quot; data-timestamp=&quot;1586193278709&quot; data-show-timestamp=&quot;true&quot; style=&quot;background-repeat: no-repeat; color: var(--secondaryTextColor); font-family: var(--secondaryHeadlineFont),Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: var(--label-1); font-weight: 700; margin-top: 10px;&quot;&gt;April 6, 2020&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/ps-promo&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;background-repeat: no-repeat; margin: 30px 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;Disneyland has been closed since March 14, the longest time the park has been shut since it opened in 1955. Typically, tickets to Disneyland and/or California Adventure Park are&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;Link&quot; href=&quot;https://disneyland.disney.go.com/faq/tickets/eticket-terms-conditions/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;background-repeat: no-repeat; touch-action: manipulation; color: var(--primaryBodyLinkColor); text-decoration-line: underline;&quot;&gt;nonrefundable and nontransferable&lt;/a&gt;. During the coronavirus-related closure, the theme park has issued additional ticket guidelines.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;background-repeat: no-repeat; margin: 30px 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&ldquo;Unused single-day tickets and wholly unused multi-day tickets are valid for a future visit through the end of their respective validity period,&rdquo; the park&rsquo;s website said. This means tickets may be used on different dates, &ldquo;depending on the type of ticket purchased, seasonal or tier.&rdquo; (In other words, if you have a Tier 1 to 5 ticket, you need to find a postponement date for the same or lower tier.)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;background-repeat: no-repeat; margin: 30px 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;The expiration date for Southern California Resident tickets will be extended by a day for each day the theme park is closed. Other rules apply to other ticket types and annual passes; check the&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;Link&quot; href=&quot;https://disneyland.disney.go.com/travel-information/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;background-repeat: no-repeat; touch-action: manipulation; color: var(--primaryBodyLinkColor); text-decoration-line: underline;&quot;&gt;website&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;for details.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;background-repeat: no-repeat; margin: 30px 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;At the moment, ticket holders may postpone their visit to June 1 and beyond. However, that timeline could be pushed deeper into summer if stay-at-home orders have not been lifted.&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;Link&quot; href=&quot;https://disneyland.disney.go.com/faq/tickets/ticket-dates/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;background-repeat: no-repeat; touch-action: manipulation; color: var(--primaryBodyLinkColor); text-decoration-line: underline;&quot;&gt;Blackout dates apply&lt;/a&gt;, depending on what ticket type you have.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;background-repeat: no-repeat; margin: 30px 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;Also, new ticket orders will not be shipped during the closure, the website says.&lt;br style=&quot;background-repeat: no-repeat;&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;Enhancement&quot; data-align-center=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;background-repeat: no-repeat; clear: both; margin: 30px 0px; width: 619px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;ps-promo class=&quot;PromoSmall&quot; data-content-type=&quot;article&quot; style=&quot;background-repeat: no-repeat; display: block; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--secondaryColor3); border-top: 1px solid var(--secondaryColor3); padding: 20px 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;PromoSmall-wrapper&quot; style=&quot;background-repeat: no-repeat; display: flex; flex-direction: row;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;PromoSmall-media&quot; style=&quot;background-repeat: no-repeat; position: relative; margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; flex-shrink: 0; max-width: 110px; order: 1; width: 110px;&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;Link&quot; aria-label=&quot;Disneyland and Walt Disney World Resort will remain closed until further notice&quot; href=&quot;https://www.latimes.com/business/story/2020-03-27/disneyland-and-walt-disney-world-resort-will-remain-closed-until-further-notice&quot; style=&quot;background-repeat: no-repeat; touch-action: manipulation; color: inherit; display: block; position: relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/ps-promo&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;background-repeat: no-repeat; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 30px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;Enhancement&quot; data-align-center=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;background-repeat: no-repeat; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; margin: 30px 0px; width: 619px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;nativo_1&quot; style=&quot;background-repeat: no-repeat; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;',16,'News-20200408060306769.jpg','Kathmandu','Guardians','state3',1,'2020-04-10 00:00:00'),(10,'Fifa set to rearrange 2021',0,'2020-04-08 16:10:47',NULL,NULL,'active','Fifa have called a council conference call for Wednesday where they will accept the postponements of Euro 2020 and Copa America 2020 until next year.','&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: 27px; font-family: &amp;quot;Independent Serif&amp;quot;, serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.independent.co.uk/topic/FIFA&quot; class=&quot;body-link&quot; data-vars-item-name=&quot;BL-9407441-/topic/FIFA&quot; data-vars-event-id=&quot;c6&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(236, 26, 46);&quot;&gt;Fifa&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;have called a council conference call for Wednesday where they will accept the postponements of&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.independent.co.uk/topic/Euro_2020&quot; class=&quot;body-link&quot; data-vars-item-name=&quot;BL-9407441-/topic/Euro_2020&quot; data-vars-event-id=&quot;c6&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(236, 26, 46);&quot;&gt;Euro 2020&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.independent.co.uk/topic/copa-america-2020&quot; class=&quot;body-link&quot; data-vars-item-name=&quot;BL-9407441-/topic/copa-america-2020&quot; data-vars-event-id=&quot;c6&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(236, 26, 46);&quot;&gt;Copa America 2020&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;until next year.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: 27px; font-family: &amp;quot;Independent Serif&amp;quot;, serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;The Club World Cup, due to be played in the summer of 2021, will also be discussed, with that tournament set to be postponed either until later in 2021, 2022 or 2023.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;mpu0ArticleBody&quot; class=&quot;ad-wrapper ad-wrapper--mobile ad-wrapper--mpu0&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Independent Serif&amp;quot;, serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; width: auto; z-index: 1; position: relative; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: 27px; font-family: &amp;quot;Independent Serif&amp;quot;, serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;In a statement from president Gianni Infantino, Fifa pledged a direct contribution of $10m to the World Health Organisation COVID-19 Solidarity Response Fund.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;thirdparty01&quot; data-google-query-id=&quot;CMfDv_Ho2OgCFVAkaAodkm8DKQ&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Independent Serif&amp;quot;, serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;google_ads_iframe_/71347885/_main_independent/in_sport/in_football/in_world/in_world_article_2__container__&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0pt none; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; width: 1px; height: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;iframe frameborder=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;https://tpc.googlesyndication.com/safeframe/1-0-37/html/container.html&quot; id=&quot;google_ads_iframe_/71347885/_main_independent/in_sport/in_football/in_world/in_world_article_2&quot; title=&quot;3rd party ad content&quot; name=&quot;&quot; scrolling=&quot;no&quot; marginwidth=&quot;0&quot; marginheight=&quot;0&quot; width=&quot;1&quot; height=&quot;1&quot; data-is-safeframe=&quot;true&quot; sandbox=&quot;allow-forms allow-pointer-lock allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation&quot; data-google-container-id=&quot;2&quot; data-load-complete=&quot;true&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; font: inherit; vertical-align: bottom; max-width: 100%;&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;ad-wrapper ad-wrapper--teads&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Independent Serif&amp;quot;, serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; width: auto; z-index: 1; position: relative; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;teads-inread&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;article-im-prompt&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Independent Serif&amp;quot;, serif; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: 27px; font-family: &amp;quot;Independent Serif&amp;quot;, serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;He said: &ldquo;To protect the interests of all stakeholders and competition organisers, whether they be national, continental or worldwide, I have called for a Bureau of the Council conference call tomorrow to see how we can progress matters collectively.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;teads-amp-ad&quot; class=&quot;ad-wrapper ad-wrapper--mobile&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Independent Serif&amp;quot;, serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; width: auto; z-index: 1; position: relative; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: 27px; font-family: &amp;quot;Independent Serif&amp;quot;, serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;&ldquo;During this call, I will suggest the following next steps: to accept the postponements of the CONMEBOL 2020 Copa America and the&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.independent.co.uk/topic/UEFA&quot; class=&quot;body-link&quot; data-vars-item-name=&quot;BL-9407441-/topic/UEFA&quot; data-vars-event-id=&quot;c6&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(236, 26, 46);&quot;&gt;UEFA&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;Euro 2020 to the June/July of 2021; to decide at a later stage &ndash; when there is more clarity on the situation &ndash; when to reschedule the new FIFA Club World Cup, later in 2021, in 2022 or in 2023.&rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;',14,'News-20200408061047213.jpg','Japan','Kantipur','state3',1,'2020-04-10 00:00:00'),(11,'NASA Selects Early-Stage Technology Concepts for New, Continued Study shows',0,'2020-04-08 16:15:59','2021-05-05 08:00:04','nasa-selects-early-stage-technology-concepts-for-new-continued-study-shows','active','Future technologies that could enable quicker trips to Mars and robotic exploration of ocean worlds might have started out as NASA Innovative Advanced Concepts (NIAC). The program, which invests in early-stage technology ideas from NASA, industry','<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Future technologies that could enable quicker trips to Mars and robotic exploration of ocean worlds might have started out as <a href=\"https://www.nasa.gov/directorates/spacetech/niac/index.html\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(66, 139, 202);\">NASA Innovative Advanced Concepts</a> (NIAC). The program, which invests in early-stage technology ideas from NASA, industry and academic researchers across the country, has selected 23 potentially revolutionary concepts with a total award value of $7 million.</p><p></p><div class=\"dnd-atom-wrapper type-image context-side_image\" contenteditable=\"false\" style=\"display: table; margin: 0.5em 0em 3em 2em; max-width: 320px; float: right; clear: right; width: 320px; font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><div class=\"dnd-drop-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://www.nasa.gov/sites/default/files/thumbnails/image/niac2020_turyshev_2.png\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(66, 139, 202);\"><img typeof=\"foaf:Image\" src=\"https://www.nasa.gov/sites/default/files/styles/side_image/public/thumbnails/image/niac2020_turyshev_2.png?itok=BCj52dSs\" width=\"320\" height=\"295\" alt=\"Illustration of how a solar gravity lens telescope would image an exoplanet.v\" title=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin-bottom: 10px;\"></a></div><div class=\"dnd-legend-wrapper\" style=\"caption-side: bottom; font-size: 11px;\"><div class=\"caption\">Illustration of how a solar gravity lens telescope would image an exoplanet. The technology concept received Phase I, II and III awards from the NASA Innovative Advanced Concepts program.</div><div class=\"credits\" style=\"font-style: italic; font-weight: bold;\">Credits: NASA JPL/Slava Turyshev</div><div class=\"link\" style=\"background: inherit; padding: 0px;\"></div></div></div><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Among the selections are 16 new concepts and seven studies that previously received at least one NIAC award. A full list of the 2020 Phase I, II and III selections can be found <a href=\"http://www.nasa.gov/directorates/spacetech/niac/2020_Phase_I_Phase_II\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(66, 139, 202);\">here</a>.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">“NIAC is an innovative program that encourages researchers – and the agency – to think outside of the box for solutions that could overcome challenges facing future science and exploration missions,” said Walt Engelund, deputy associate administrator for programs within NASA’s Space Technology Mission Directorate (STMD). “We’re excited about the new concepts and to see how additional time and resources advances the research selected for follow-on Phase II and III studies.”</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">A mission concept to image Earth-like planets outside of the solar system was selected for a Phase III study. Slava Turyshev, a researcher at NASA’s Jet Propulsion Laboratory in Pasadena, California, will receive a $2 million grant to further mature the concept and related technologies.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">During his <a href=\"https://www.nasa.gov/directorates/spacetech/niac/2017_Phase_I_Phase_II/Solar_Gravity_Lens_Mission\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(66, 139, 202);\">Phase I</a> and <a href=\"https://www.nasa.gov/directorates/spacetech/niac/2018_Phase_I_Phase_II/Direct_Multipixel_Imaging_and_Spectroscopy\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(66, 139, 202);\">Phase II</a> NIAC research, Turyshev outlined the feasibility of a solar gravity lens to enable enhanced viewing of planets orbiting other stars, known as <a href=\"https://exoplanets.nasa.gov/what-is-an-exoplanet/about-exoplanets/\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(66, 139, 202);\">exoplanets</a>. He also developed a mission architecture that uses multiple small spacecraft and solar sail technology to propel them to their target destination 50 billion miles from Earth.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">“This is only the <a href=\"https://www.nasa.gov/press-release/nasa-invests-in-tech-concepts-aimed-at-exploring-lunar-craters-mining-asteroids\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(66, 139, 202);\">third study</a> selected for Phase III funding in the history of the program,” said NIAC Program Executive Jason Derleth. “We’re excited by its potential to bring us closer to imaging an exoplanet in detail, at a resolution comparable to the well-known Apollo 8 <a href=\"https://www.nasa.gov/image-feature/apollo-8-earthrise\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(66, 139, 202);\">Earthrise</a> photo.”</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">The selected Phase I and II studies will explore the overall viability of a technology and develop them into mission concepts. Areas researchers will study include mapping asteroids and other small bodies in the solar system with hopping probes, making on-demand pharmaceuticals in space, and extracting water on the Moon. Several of the concepts could inform capabilities relevant to NASA’s <a href=\"https://www.nasa.gov/specials/artemis/\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(66, 139, 202);\">Artemis</a> program, which will land the first woman and next man on the Moon in 2024 and establish a sustainable presence on and around the Moon by 2028.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">NASA selected the proposals through a peer-review process that evaluates innovation and technical viability. All projects are still in the early stages of development, with most requiring a decade or more of technology maturation, and are not official NASA missions.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">NIAC supports visionary research ideas through multiple progressive phases of study. Phase I studies receive $125,000 and are nine-month efforts. Eligible recipients of Phase I awards can submit proposals for a follow-on Phase II study. Selected Phase II researchers receive $500,000 grants to further develop their concepts for up to two years. Phase III is designed to strategically transition NIAC concepts with the highest potential impact for NASA other government agencies or commercial partners. Phase III researchers receive $2 million grants to develop and mature their mission concept over two years.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">NIAC is funded by STMD, which is responsible for developing the new cross-cutting technologies and capabilities needed by the agency to achieve its current and future missions.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">For more information about NASA’s investments in space technology, visit:</p>',3,'News-20200408061559185.jpg','Kathmandu','NASA report','all',0,'2020-04-10 00:00:00'),(12,'trump says US will have more ventilators than it needs',0,'2020-04-08 16:51:44','2021-05-05 08:08:56','trump-says-us-will-have-more-ventilators-than-it-needs','active','President Donald Trump says the US will soon have more ventilators than it needs to help those suffering with coronavirus across the country.','<p class=\"story-body__introduction\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.375; margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">President Donald Trump says the US will soon have more ventilators than it needs to help those suffering with coronavirus across the country.</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin: 23px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">The US \"won\'t need anywhere near\" the additional 110,000 devices that it will have at its disposal, he said.</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin: 18px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">He added that any surplus could be distributed among \"desperate\" countries fighting the virus, including the UK.</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin: 18px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Mr Trump also threatened to end funding for the World Health Organization over its handling of the pandemic.</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin: 18px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">The president accused the United Nations agency of being biased towards China while issuing its guidance during the coronavirus outbreak.</p><ul class=\"story-body__unordered-list\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 18px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none;\"><li class=\"story-body__list-item\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.375; margin: 18px 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 4px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: outside square;\"><a href=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/live/world-52208591\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.375; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">LIVE: Wuhan\'s 11-week lockdown finally ends</a></li></ul><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin: 18px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">His remarks came as&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-us-canada-52209954\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.375; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">the US recorded a daily death toll from Covid-19 of more than 1,800</a>. The country has nearly 400,000 known infections, according to figures compiled by Johns Hopkins University.</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin: 18px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">New York state, one of the worst affected areas, is on the cusp of overtaking the entire country of Italy in its confirmed number of coronavirus cases.</p><h2 class=\"story-body__crosshead\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.16667; margin: 32px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">What did Trump say?</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin: 18px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Speaking during the daily Coronavirus Task Force briefing at the White House on Tuesday, Mr Trump said the US had 8,675 ventilators in a national stockpile, with \"a total of 110,000 ventilators coming over a short period of time\".</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin: 18px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">However he said the majority, some 60,000 devices, would not be received until 29 June.</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin: 18px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">\"I don\'t think we\'ll need them,\" he said, \"but we\'ll have them for the future, and we\'ll also be able to help other countries who are desperate for ventilators\".</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin: 18px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">The president said the UK had already requested 200 devices, adding: \"We\'re going to work it out, we\'ve got to work it out - they\'ve been great partners, the United Kingdom.\"</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin: 18px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Ventilators are vital in the treatment of some patients suffering from coronavirus, which can cause severe respiratory issues while the infection attacks the lungs. The devices can help keep patients breathing.</p><ul class=\"story-body__unordered-list\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 18px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none;\"><li class=\"story-body__list-item\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.375; margin: 18px 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 4px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: outside square;\"><a href=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/health-52036948\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.375; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">What are ventilators and why are they important?</a></li></ul><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin: 18px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">On the funding of the World Health Organization (WHO), Mr Trump said there would be a \"hold on money\" provided to the UN agency, which he accused of being \"very China-centric\".</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin: 18px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">He tweeted that his administration would take \"a good look\" at its contributions and questioned some of the advice the WHO had provided in tackling the coronavirus.</p><p><figure class=\"media-landscape no-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin-top: 24px; margin-right: -24.6406px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"></span></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 1.375; margin: 18px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">\"Fortunately I rejected their advice on keeping our borders open to China early on,\" he said. \"Why did they give us such a faulty recommendation?\"</p>',11,'News-20200408065144350.jpg','Kathmandu','BBC','all',1,'2020-10-07 00:00:00'),(13,'Coronavirus: Boris Johnson \'responding to treatment\' in intensive care',0,'2020-04-08 16:55:10',NULL,NULL,'active','Boris Johnson is \"responding to treatment\" for coronavirus as he spends his third day in hospital.','&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin: 23px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;The prime minister was being kept in St Thomas\' Hospital in London &quot;for close monitoring&quot; and remained clinically stable, Downing Street said.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin: 18px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Downing Street said he was not working but could contact those he needed to.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin: 18px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;No 10 said a review of lockdown rules would go ahead as planned next week, but the public must &quot;stick with&quot; the measures at what was a &quot;critical time&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin: 18px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;A ban on public gatherings of more than two people and the closure of shops selling non-essential goods were among the series of restrictions&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-52014472&quot; class=&quot;story-body__link&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.375; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);&quot;&gt;announced by Mr Johnson on 23 March&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;to tackle the spread of coronavirus.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin: 18px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Downing Street said a relaxation of the rules would be considered &quot;on or around&quot; the three-week mark on Monday, as was promised by the PM when he introduced the measures.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin: 18px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;But health minister Edward Argar said the peak in cases must pass &quot;before we can think about making changes&quot;, adding: &quot;It\'s too early to say when we will reach that peak.&quot;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin: 18px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;The prime minister was admitted to St Thomas\' on Sunday, on the advice of his doctor, after continuing to display symptoms of a cough and high temperature 10 days after testing positive for the virus.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin: 18px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Downing Street said Mr Johnson was in &quot;good spirits&quot; as he continued to receive standard oxygen treatment. He was breathing without any assistance, such as mechanical ventilation or non-invasive respiratory support.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin: 18px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;The Queen and&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/KensingtonRoyal/status/1247517948962467841&quot; class=&quot;story-body__link-external&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.375; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);&quot;&gt;other senior royals&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;sent messages to Mr Johnson\'s family and his pregnant fiancee, Carrie Symonds, saying they were thinking of them, and wished the PM a full and speedy recovery.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin: 18px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Foreign Secretary Dominic Raab, who is deputising for Mr Johnson, said on Tuesday he was&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-52201048&quot; class=&quot;story-body__link&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.375; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);&quot;&gt;&quot;confident&quot; the PM would recover from this illness&lt;/a&gt;, describing him as a &quot;fighter&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin: 18px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;The lockdown in Wales will be extended and not lifted next week,&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-wales-52215421&quot; class=&quot;story-body__link&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.375; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);&quot;&gt;First Minister Mark Drakeford has confirmed&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;figure class=&quot;media-landscape no-caption full-width&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin-top: 24px; margin-right: -24.6406px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;image-and-copyright-container&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 1.375; margin: 18px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;He said there were signs people staying at home was &quot;having an impact&quot; but &quot;the efforts we are making are not over yet&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;',11,'News-20200408065510989.jpg','Kathmandu','BBC','all',1,'2020-04-07 00:00:00'),(14,'Coronavirus: EU top scientist forced out in political row',0,'2020-04-08 17:15:58',NULL,NULL,'active','The president of the European Union\'s ERC scientific research council has resigned after three months in the job with an attack on the EU\'s scientific governance and political operations.','&lt;p class=&quot;story-body__introduction&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.375; margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;The president of the European Union\'s ERC scientific research council has resigned after three months in the job with an attack on the EU\'s scientific governance and political operations.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin: 23px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Mauro Ferrari said he had lost faith in the system after he failed to set up a special programme to fight coronavirus.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin: 18px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;But the research council said later his resignation followed a written, unanimous vote of no confidence.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin: 18px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;It said it regretted Prof Ferrari\'s comments.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin: 18px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;&quot;Since his appointment, Professor Ferrari displayed a lack of engagement with the ERC, failing to participate in many important meetings, spending extensive time in the USA and failing to defend the ERC\'s programme and mission when representing the ERC,&quot;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://erc.europa.eu/news/resignation-mauro-ferrari-%E2%80%93-statement-scientific-council&quot; class=&quot;story-body__link-external&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.375; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);&quot;&gt;it said in a statement&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin: 18px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;The EU\'s executive insisted it had the most comprehensive measures to combat the virus.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin: 18px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;One MEP had earlier been quoted accusing Prof Ferrari of taking a &quot;window-dressing public relations stand&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 class=&quot;story-body__crosshead&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.16667; margin: 32px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Who is Mauro Ferrari?&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin: 18px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Mauro Ferrari is an Italian-American scientist known as a pioneer in the field of nanomedicine with decades of work in the US. When he took up the role as head of the European Research Council he stressed his commitment to serving society.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin: 18px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;In a statement to the Financial Times and Corriere della Sera in Italy,&lt;a href=&quot;http://prod-upp-image-read.ft.com/65f5a27e-78dd-11ea-af44-daa3def9ae03&quot; class=&quot;story-body__link-external&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.375; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;he spoke of his commitment to the &quot;idealistic dream of a United Europe&lt;/a&gt;... crushed by a very different reality&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin: 18px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;As the tragedy of the pandemic became clear Prof Ferrari says he pushed for a special programme directed at combating Covid-19, with the world\'s best scientists having the resources to fight it with new drugs, vaccines, diagnostic tools and behavioural approaches based on sciences &quot;to replace the oft-improvised intuitions of political leaders&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helmet, Freesans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.375; margin: 18px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;His proposals were rejected unanimously, he said, by the council\'s governing body because the ERC funded &quot;bottom-up&quot; research proposed by scientists themselves and did not see the beneficial impact on society as a justification for funding.&lt;/p&gt;',11,'News-20200408071558617.jpg','Kathmandu','BBC','state1',1,'2020-04-07 00:00:00'),(15,'John Cena vs The Fiend: Who put together the ‘Firefly Fun House’ match at WrestleMania?',0,'2020-04-08 23:58:33',NULL,NULL,'active','The 16-time World Champion John Cena had a bizarre encounter against the Fiend Bray Wyatt at WrestleMania 36.','&lt;p style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; list-style-type: none; outline: 0px; font-family: &amp;quot;PT Serif&amp;quot;, serif; border: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: 20px; line-height: 32px;&quot;&gt;The WrestleMania 36 will surely go down in history as one of the most memorable ones. After all, it was for the first time, the Show of Shows was held behind closed doors at a WWE Performance Center in Florida, in front of no fans. The reason - the outbreak of novel coronavirus in USA. It was also for the first time that the show was divided into two nights - and was pre-taped, instead of being performed live. This allowed WWE to put on some creative changes to the product, the pinnacle of which were the Boneyard match between AJ Styles and The Undertaker, and the Firefly Fun House match between The Fiend Bray Wyatt and 16-time World Champion.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; list-style-type: none; outline: 0px; font-family: &amp;quot;PT Serif&amp;quot;, serif; border: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: 20px; line-height: 32px;&quot;&gt;While the boneyard match has received positive feedback from most quarters, and is being hailed as the Phenom&rsquo;s best match in recent years, not everyone bought into the Firefly Fun House segment.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; list-style-type: none; outline: 0px; font-family: &amp;quot;PT Serif&amp;quot;, serif; border: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: 20px; line-height: 32px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style-type: none; outline: 0px; font-family: &amp;quot;Open Sans&amp;quot;, sans-serif; border: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Also read:&thinsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.hindustantimes.com/other-sports/wwe-wrestlemania-36-bray-wyatt-vs-john-cena-was-nothing-like-we-have-seen-before-it-was-a-cinematic-marvel/story-ovQKaYlezwWtj0qFKSZ5aP.html&quot; title=&quot;Bray Wyatt vs John Cena at WWE WrestleMania 36 was nothing short of a cinematic marvel&quot; style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style-type: none; outline: 0px; font-family: &amp;quot;PT Serif&amp;quot;, serif; border: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(3, 110, 174);&quot;&gt;Bray Wyatt vs John Cena at WWE WrestleMania 36 was nothing short of a cinematic marvel&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; list-style-type: none; outline: 0px; font-family: &amp;quot;PT Serif&amp;quot;, serif; border: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: 20px; line-height: 32px;&quot;&gt;The match was not actually a fight, but a series of vignettes, which tried to portray John Cena as a &ldquo;controversial figure&rdquo; in the industry, who is having to face his own &ldquo;demons&rdquo;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; list-style-type: none; outline: 0px; font-family: &amp;quot;PT Serif&amp;quot;, serif; border: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: 20px; line-height: 32px;&quot;&gt;In the match, Cena goes through Wyatt&rsquo;s Fun House, and gets trapped in an alternate world, where he has to face his own past - his debut, him almost getting fired, his not-so-succesful rap career, his worries about not having a big body, and constant comparisons with Hulk Hogan, as both the wrestlers were known for back-door politics to ensure they emerge as winners. At one point, Wyatt even sang Cena&rsquo;s ex-fiance Nikki Bella&rsquo;s theme song - &ldquo;You can look but you can&rsquo;t touch&rsquo;. The Fiend emerged victorious in the end, as Cena was literally evaporated into thin air.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; list-style-type: none; outline: 0px; font-family: &amp;quot;PT Serif&amp;quot;, serif; border: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: 20px; line-height: 32px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style-type: none; outline: 0px; font-family: &amp;quot;Open Sans&amp;quot;, sans-serif; border: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Also read:&thinsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.hindustantimes.com/other-sports/drew-mcintyre-conquers-the-conquerer-brock-lesnar-at-wwe-wrestlemania-36/story-CX3dBoesB8eclwSC23tR3N.html&quot; title=&quot;McIntyre tamed the &lsquo;Beast&rsquo; Brock Lesnar at WWE WrestleMania 36 and fulfilled a prophecy&quot; style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style-type: none; outline: 0px; font-family: &amp;quot;PT Serif&amp;quot;, serif; border: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(3, 110, 174);&quot;&gt;McIntyre tamed the &lsquo;Beast&rsquo; Brock Lesnar at WWE WrestleMania 36 and fulfilled a prophecy&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; list-style-type: none; outline: 0px; font-family: &amp;quot;PT Serif&amp;quot;, serif; border: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: 20px; line-height: 32px;&quot;&gt;Wrestling Observer Radio&rsquo;s Dave Meltzer has reported on who were the creative force behind coming up with the bizarre segment. In his latest podcast, Meltzer reported that SmackDown&rsquo;s Executive Director Bruch Prichard and Bray Wyatt largely came up with the segment, with John Cena making a few suggestions as well..&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; list-style-type: none; outline: 0px; font-family: &amp;quot;PT Serif&amp;quot;, serif; border: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: 20px; line-height: 32px;&quot;&gt;Meltzer further reported that Cena mostly made a few suggestions in the match, which improved the overall segment, but did not specify which changes were made.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; list-style-type: none; outline: 0px; font-family: &amp;quot;PT Serif&amp;quot;, serif; border: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: 20px; line-height: 32px;&quot;&gt;Irrespective of how the fans will feel about the segment - it is bound to go down as one of the most memorable WrestleMania moments, for sure.&lt;/p&gt;',14,'News-20200409015833131.jpg','Kathmandu','Hindustan Times','state1',1,'2020-10-09 00:00:00'),(16,'Coronavirus in the US: Latest COVID-19 news and case counts',0,'2020-04-12 22:55:31',NULL,NULL,'active','Since the novel coronavirus called SARS-CoV-2 was first detected in the U.S. on Jan. 20, it has spread to more than 530,000 people in the U.S., across all 50 states.','&lt;p style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: &amp;quot;Open Sans&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; width: 602px; height: auto; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot;&gt;Since the novel coronavirus called SARS-CoV-2 was first detected in the U.S. on Jan. 20, it has spread to more than 530,000 people in the U.S., across all 50 states.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;aside class=&quot;hawk-widget&quot; data-render-type=&quot;fte&quot; data-widget-type=&quot;seasonal&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Open Sans&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; --black:#000; --white:#fff; --yellow:#ffd800; --green:#3c8d0d; --orange:#ff6f28; --red:red; --pink:#e6248a; --light-grey:#eaeaea; --grey:#adadad; --light-mid-grey:#ccc; --prime-blue:#00aeef; --trd-blue:#2f6e91; --trd-grey:#ededed; --site-color:#5aaf0b; --editors-pick-promo-color:var(--trd-blue); --review-background:var(--trd-grey); --product-label-background:var(--light-grey); --product-label-text-color:var(--black); --was-price-text-color:#848484; --was-price-promo-color:#be0707; --was-price-light-promo-color:#ededed; --was-price-light-promo-text-color:#be0707; width: 602px; --light-blue:#97edfc; --mid-grey:#333; --dark-grey:#545454; --prime-green:#eaf7e9; --lighter-mid-grey:#ebebeb; --game-platform-grey:#dbddde; --amazon-orange:#ffce00; --amazon-prime-day-blue:#70b7d9; --error-red:#f33f3f; --playstation-blue:#003791; --xbox-green:#107c10; --nintendo-red:#e60012; --trd-pink:#e6248a; --trd-light-pink:#ea489d; --trd-dark-grey:#333; --trd-dark-blue:#315062; --rose-gold:#b76e79; --heading-color:#2f6e91; --tab-color:var(--trd-blue); --cc-border-color:var(--light-mid-grey); --expanded-row-color:var(--trd-blue); --expanded-row-box-shadow:4px 4px 20px var(--expanded-row-color); --toggle-color:var(--trd-blue); --toggle-switch-color:var(--trd-blue); --editors-pick-background-color:#ededed; --editors-pick-promo-rgba-color:rgba(47,110,145,0.3); --editors-pick-voucher-background-color:#e6248a; --model-options-filter-color:var(--pink); --filter-border-color:#c1c1c1; --filter-hover-border-color:#535353; --filter-selected-hover-border-color:#666; --review-filters-border-color:var(--filter-border-color); --countdown-in-progress-color:var(--trd-pink); --rows-background-color:var(--white); --mpu-header-height:19px; --mpu-header-background:none; --mpu-header-padding:10px 0; --hawk-footer-background:var(--trd-grey); --hawk-footer-game-platform-border:solid 1px var(--game-platform-grey); --site-logo-width:100%; --site-logo-max-width:none; --hawk-tab-text-color:#666; --hawk-tab-background:#d6d6d6; --review-rows-background:var(--white); --review-peacock-background:var(--white); --seasonal-event-grey:#797979; --seasonal-event-dark-grey:#313131; --seasonal-event-merchants-background:var(--white); --game-platform-background:transparent; --price-widget-padding:none; --price-widget-border-bottom:none; --postcode-entry-button-color:var(--site-color); --dotw-header-border-top:1px solid #ddd; --dotw-header-border-bottom:4px solid #006ea9; --dotw-toggle-background-color:#1b1b1b; --dotw-search-input-border-color:#ddd; --dotw-header-background:transparent; --dotw-header-text-color:var(--black); --shopping-partners-header-background-color:#f26722; --hover-panel-color:orange; --tv-channels-display-label-color:#696969; --shop-window-border-color:#cac7c7; --user-input-color:#c1c1c1; --user-input-hover-color:#535353; --user-input-input-background:#f2f2f2; --user-input-input-error-color:#838383; --radio-button-color:#c1c1c1; --checkbox-color:#c1c1c1; --range-filter-shadow-color:#a9a9a9; --index-color:#999; --comparison-load-more-background-color:#262626; --pre-order-promise-color:#aaa; --description-hover-background:#cac7c7; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;hawk-master-widget-browser-container&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/aside&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: &amp;quot;Open Sans&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; width: 602px; height: auto; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot;&gt;Of the reported cases in the U.S., at least 20,608 people have died as a result of the virus, with at least 8,650 of those deaths in New York, more than 2,180 in&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.livescience.com/new-jersey-coronavirus-updates.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-component-tracked=&quot;11&quot; class=&quot;hawk-link-parsed&quot; data-dimension73=&quot;4494775022160845300&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(2, 108, 162);&quot;&gt;New Jersey&lt;/a&gt;, nearly 1,384 in&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.livescience.com/michigan-coronavirus.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-component-tracked=&quot;11&quot; class=&quot;hawk-link-parsed&quot; data-dimension73=&quot;1183052085239181300&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(2, 108, 162);&quot;&gt;Michigan&lt;/a&gt;, 806 in&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.livescience.com/louisiana-coronavirus-updates.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-component-tracked=&quot;11&quot; class=&quot;hawk-link-parsed&quot; data-dimension73=&quot;1048388877029077200&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(2, 108, 162);&quot;&gt;Louisiana&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;and about 634 related deaths reported in&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.livescience.com/california-coronavirus-updates.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-component-tracked=&quot;11&quot; class=&quot;hawk-link-parsed&quot; data-dimension73=&quot;5697161467601980000&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(2, 108, 162);&quot;&gt;California&lt;/a&gt;. Worldwide, about 1.8 million cases have been reported and 110,042 related deaths, according to the Johns Hopkins virus dashboard.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: &amp;quot;Open Sans&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; width: 602px; height: auto; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot;&gt;&mdash;Cases of&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.livescience.com/coronavirus-new-york.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-component-tracked=&quot;11&quot; class=&quot;hawk-link-parsed&quot; data-dimension73=&quot;8244977103768476000&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(2, 108, 162);&quot;&gt;COVID-19 in New York&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;continue to rise, with Gov. Andrew Cuomo saying that on Wednesday (April 8) the state reported 799 coronavirus-related deaths, which was the third straight day with single-day death records being hit. The next day saw 777 related deaths.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: &amp;quot;Open Sans&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; width: 602px; height: auto; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot;&gt;&mdash;The number newly hospitalized COVID-19 patients in New York has started to level off; the number had been growing by about 20% per day, but between Wednesday and Thursday (April 9), it grew by just 1%, The New York Times reported.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: &amp;quot;Open Sans&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; width: 602px; height: auto; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot;&gt;&mdash;A model that had estimated the number of COVID-19-related deaths in the U.S.&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.livescience.com/coronavirus-could-kill-hundred-thousand.html&quot; data-component-tracked=&quot;11&quot; class=&quot;hawk-link-parsed&quot; data-dimension73=&quot;6982230304896617000&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(2, 108, 162);&quot;&gt;to range from 100,000 to 240,000&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;has been revised and is now forecasting a death toll by Aug. 4 to be around 60,415, with a peak in daily deaths of 2,212 on April 12.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;slot-single-height-14-506&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Open Sans&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); position: relative; height: 0px; text-align: center; pointer-events: none;&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: &amp;quot;Open Sans&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; width: 602px; height: auto; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot;&gt;&mdash;Infectious diseases expert Dr. Anthony Fauci said Friday morning (April 10) that in about a week an antibody test would become available to show who has already been infected with the novel coronavirus, The &amp;nbsp;New York Times reported.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;slot-single-height-13-273&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Open Sans&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); position: relative; height: 0px; text-align: center; pointer-events: none;&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: &amp;quot;Open Sans&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; width: 602px; height: auto; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot;&gt;&lt;em style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;&mdash;&lt;/em&gt;Just eight states have governors who have held out on issuing state-wide stay-at-home orders for all residents, according to&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2020/us/coronavirus-stay-at-home-order.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-component-tracked=&quot;11&quot; class=&quot;hawk-link-parsed&quot; data-dimension73=&quot;3752486487544047000&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(2, 108, 162);&quot;&gt;The New York Times&lt;/a&gt;, despite calls to do so. These states include: Arkansas, Iowa, Nebraska, North Dakota, Oklahoma, South Dakota, Utah and Wyoming.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: &amp;quot;Open Sans&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; width: 602px; height: auto; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot;&gt;&lt;iframe width=&quot;600&quot; height=&quot;400&quot; scrolling=&quot;no&quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot; data-lazy-priority=&quot;low&quot; data-lazy-src=&quot;//datawrapper.dwcdn.net/lnKyw/1/&quot; data-lazy-report=&quot;lazily loaded with low priority&quot; src=&quot;https://datawrapper.dwcdn.net/lnKyw/1/&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 100%;&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id=&quot;coronavirus-memo&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.7em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 30px; font-family: &amp;quot;Open Sans&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; vertical-align: baseline; width: 602px; height: auto; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot;&gt;Coronavirus memo&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;slot-double-height-10-1530&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Open Sans&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); position: relative; height: 0px; text-align: center; pointer-events: none;&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: &amp;quot;Open Sans&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; width: 602px; height: auto; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot;&gt;Two memorandums sent to President Donald Trump and the National Security Council by trade advisor Peter Navarro lay out alarming forecasts for how hard the spreading coronavirus could hit Americans, according to news sites that obtained the memos. In a memo dated Jan. 29 that was sent to the National Security Council, Navarro writes: &quot;The lack of immune protection or an existing cure or vaccine would leave Americans defenseless in the case of a full-blown coronavirus outbreak on U.S. soil. ... This lack of protection elevates the risk of the coronavirus evolving into a full-blown pandemic, imperiling the lives of millions of Americans,&quot;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.nytimes.com/2020/04/07/world/coronavirus-updates-news-live.html#link-63232720&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-component-tracked=&quot;11&quot; class=&quot;hawk-link-parsed&quot; data-dimension73=&quot;1235473107648006100&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(2, 108, 162);&quot;&gt;The New York Times reported&lt;/a&gt;. In one of the worst-case scenarios that Navarro described, more than half a million Americans could die from the disease, the Times reported.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;slot-single-height-12-715&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Open Sans&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); position: relative; height: 0px; text-align: center; pointer-events: none;&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: &amp;quot;Open Sans&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; width: 602px; height: auto; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot;&gt;The other memo, dated Feb. 23 and addressed to President Trump, is also attributed to Navarro. In the memo, according to&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2020/04/07/coronavirus-peter-navarro-warned-coronavirus-january-february/2959826001/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-component-tracked=&quot;11&quot; class=&quot;hawk-link-parsed&quot; data-dimension73=&quot;1062148559555119100&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(2, 108, 162);&quot;&gt;Axios&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;and the Times, Navarro indicates the need for resources from Congress.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;slot-single-height-11-518&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Open Sans&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); position: relative; height: 0px; text-align: center; pointer-events: none;&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: &amp;quot;Open Sans&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; width: 602px; height: auto; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot;&gt;&quot;This is NOT a time for penny-pinching or horse trading on the Hill,&quot; Navarro wrote, as reported by Axios. The memo also warned that an&amp;nbsp;&ldquo;increasing probability of a full-blown COVID-19 pandemic that could infect as many as 100 million Americans, with a loss of life of as many as 1.2 million souls.&quot;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: &amp;quot;Open Sans&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; width: 602px; height: auto; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot;&gt;At the time of both memos, the president was downplaying the severity of the not-yet-pandemic situation. In a tweet dated to Feb. 24, Trump wrote: &quot;The Coronavirus is very much under control in the USA,&quot; Axios reported.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;',11,'News-20200413125531631.jpg','Kathmandu','BBC','state1',1,'2020-04-11 00:00:00');
/*!40000 ALTER TABLE `news_posts` ENABLE KEYS */;
UNLOCK TABLES;

